headline: Morgan Stanley Reduces PT on Tenaya Therapeutics (TNYA), Keeps Constructive Stance on U.S. Small- to Mid-Cap Biotech
summary: Tenaya Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:TNYA) is one of the stocks under $1 that will explode. On January 8, 2026, TheFly reported that Morgan Stanley reduced its price target on Tenaya Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:TNYA) from $5 to $2, while reiterating an ‘Overweight’ rating.
